We are an Independent Family run restaurant on Castle Street
serving locals and visitors in the UK and worldwide. All our
dishes are Handmade on our premises using Hong Kong culinary
skills. If you require help with menu choice or have any special
requests please ask our friendly Staff. Enjoy your meal.
